### Get all WorkspaceStatuses
GET {{baseUrl}}/workspace-status

?? status == 200

### Get WorkspaceStatus by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/workspace-status/{{workspaceStatusId}}

?? status == 200

### Update WorkspaceStatus
